:"2019-12-10T14:37:20.000Z","msg":"多謝你"},{"pid":"99c40abd62707408e9ed095feaad6a77fdca031e","tid":1777678,"uid":13160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:37:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c52f4f4bf675db771ed31a30a1b7c8fb19fcf2a2","tid":1777678,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尋找黑警性暴力證人/受害者，協助國際遊說</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2640629789347426%26id%3D124616407615456&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cYBs3SnDZqPj3JJ4J4HclPc%3D&h=7e12c493\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456</a><br />\n<br />\nPost：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eDEkrT\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eDEkrT</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"7702976e6eaaacd0317851ac14151c7423be7a51","tid":1777678,"uid":13160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:41:02.000Z","msg":"得啲電腦回覆"},{"pid":"723d18d7fcbac93d0d1d55dcb7be79a964980189","tid":1777678,"uid":331459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:43:40.000Z","msg":"Sorry, 借個位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">[集思廣益] 初一15 plan</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1777893\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1777893</a>"},{"pid":"8370f9effc03dbfbfc5c9fe61d1b0865d42c0f49","tid":1777678,"uid":82935,"like